<li>Publication date</li>
<li>AI tool used (if known)</li>
<li>Level of human editing (Tier 2, 3, 4, or 5 from the Compliance Spectrum)</li>
<li>Word count</li>
<li>Traffic trend (growing, stable, or declining over the last 3 months)</li>
</ul>
